quran[3]{c,v,t}:
  55,0,shuru allah ka naam le kar jo bara meharban nihayat reham wala hai
  55,1,( khuda jo ) nihayat meharban
  55,2,isi ne quran ki taleem farmai
  55,3,isi ne ensaan ko pedakiya
  55,4,isi ne is ko bolna sikhaya
  55,5,Sooraj aur chaand aik hisaab muqarrar se chal rahay hain
  55,6,aur bootiyan aur darakht sajda kar rahay hain
  55,7,aur isi ne aasman ko bulandkiya aur traazo qaim ki
  55,8,ke traazo ( se tolnay ) mein hadd se tajawaz nah karo
  55,9,aur insaaf ke sath theek tolo. aur toal kam mat karo
  55,10,aur isi ne khalqat ke liye zameen bichai
  55,11,is mein meway aur khajoor ke darakht hain jin ke khoshon par ghilaaf hotay hain
  55,12,aur anaaj jis ke sath bhus hota hai aur khushbodar phool
  55,13,to ( ae giroh jin o ins ) tum apne perwar-digaar ki kon kon si Nemat ko jhutlao ge ?
  55,14,isi ne ensaan kotehkray ki terhan khanlhanti matti se banaya
  55,15,aur jaanat ko aag ke sholay se pedakiya
  55,16,to tum apne perwar-digaar ki kon kon si Nemat ko jhutlao ge ?
  55,17,wohi dono mashriqon aur dono maghrabon ka maalik ( hai )
  55,18,to tum apne perwar-digaar ki kon kon si Nemat ko jhutlao ge ?
  55,19,isi ne do darya rawan kiye jo aapas mein mlitay hain
  55,20,dono mein aik aarr hai ke ( is se ) tajawaz nahi kar saktay
  55,21,to tum apne perwar-digaar ki kon kon si Nemat ko jhutlao ge ?
  55,22,dono daryaaon se moti aur mongay nikaltay hain
  55,23,to tum apne perwar-digaar ki kon kon si Nemat ko jhutlao ge ?
  55,24,aur jahaaz bhi isi ke hain jo darya mein pahoron ki terhan ounchay kharray hotay hain
  55,25,to tum apne perwar-digaar ki kon kon si Nemat ko jhutlao ge ?
  55,26,jo ( makhlooq ) zameen par hai sab ko fanaa hona hai
  55,27,aur tumahray perwar-digaar hi ki zaat (ba barkaat ) jo sahib jalal vazmt hai baqi rahay gi
  55,28,to tum apne perwar-digaar ki kon kon si Nemat ko jhutlao ge ?
  55,29,aasman aur zameen mein jitne log hain sab isi se mangte hain. woh har roz kaam mein masroof rehta hai
  55,30,to tum apne perwar-digaar ki kon kon si Nemat ko jhutlao ge ?
  55,31,ae dono jmaato! hum anqareeb tumhari taraf mutwajjah hotay hain
  55,32,to tum apne perwar-digaar ki kon kon si Nemat ko jhutlao ge ?
  55,33,ae giroh jin o ins agar tumhe qudrat ho ke aasman aur zameen ke kinaroon se nikal jao to nikal jao. aur zor ke siwa tum nikal saknay hi ke nahi
  55,34,to tum apne perwar-digaar ki kon kon si Nemat ko jhutlao ge ?
  55,35,tum par aag ke sholay aur dhuwan chore diya jaye ga to phir tum muqaabla nah krsko ge
  55,36,to tum apne perwar-digaar ki kon kon si Nemat ko jhutlao ge ?
  55,37,phir jab aasman phatt kar tail ki tilchat ki terhan gulaabii hojaye ga ( to ) woh kaisa holnaak din hoga
  55,38,to tum apne perwar-digaar ki kon kon si Nemat ko jhutlao ge ?
  55,39,is roz nah to kisi ensaan se is ke gunaaho ke baray mein prssh ki jaye gi aur nah kisi jin se
  55,40,to tum apne perwar-digaar ki kon kon si Nemat ko jhutlao ge ?
  55,41,gunehgaar apne chehray hi se pehchan liye jayen ge to peshani ke balon aur paon se pakar liye jayen ge
  55,42,to tum apne perwar-digaar ki kon kon si Nemat ko jhutlao ge ?
  55,43,yahi woh jahannum hai jisay gunehgaar log jutlatay they
  55,44,woh dozakh aur kholtey hue garam pani ke darmain ghumte phrin ge
  55,45,to tum apne perwar-digaar ki kon kon si Nemat ko jhutlao ge ?
  55,46,aur jo shakhs apne perwar-digaar ke samnay kharray honay se dara is ke liye do baagh hain
  55,47,to tum apne perwar-digaar ki kon kon si Nemat ko jhutlao ge ?
  55,48,un dono mein bohat si shaakhen ( yani qisam qisam ke khushkabriyan ke darakht hain )
  55,49,to tum apne perwar-digaar ki kon kon si Nemat ko jhutlao ge ?
  55,50,un mein do chashmay beh rahay hain
  55,51,to tum apne perwar-digaar ki kon kon si Nemat ko jhutlao ge ?
  55,52,un mein sab meway do do qisam ke hain
  55,53,to tum apne perwar-digaar ki kon kon si Nemat ko jhutlao ge ?
  55,54,( ahal jannat ) aisay bichonon par jin ke astar atlas ke hain takiya lagaye hue hon ge. aur dono baghoon ke meway qareeb ( jhuk rahay ) hain
  55,55,to tum apne perwar-digaar ki kon kon si Nemat ko jhutlao ge ?
  55,56,un mein neechi nigah wali aurtain hain jin ko ahal jannat se pehlay nah kisi ensaan ne haath lagaya aur nah kisi jin ne
  55,57,to tum apne perwar-digaar ki kon kon si Nemat ko jhutlao ge ?
  55,58,goya woh Yaqoot aur Marjaan hain
  55,59,to tum apne perwar-digaar ki kon kon si Nemat ko jhutlao ge ?
  55,60,neki ka badla neki ke siwa kuch nahi hai
  55,61,to tum apne perwar-digaar ki kon kon si Nemat ko jhutlao ge ?
  55,62,aur un baghoon ke ilawa do baagh aur hain
  55,63,to tum apne perwar-digaar ki kon kon si Nemat ko jhutlao ge ?
  55,64,dono khoob gehray sabz
  55,65,to tum apne perwar-digaar ki kon kon si Nemat ko jhutlao ge ?
  55,66,un mein do chashmay ubal rahay hain
  55,67,to tum apne perwar-digaar ki kon kon si Nemat ko jhutlao ge ?
  55,68,un mein meway aur khjorin aur aanar hain
  55,69,to tum apne perwar-digaar ki kon kon si Nemat ko jhutlao ge ?
  55,70,un mein naik seerat ( aur ) khobsorat aurtain hain
  55,71,to tum apne perwar-digaar ki kon kon si Nemat ko jhutlao ge ?
  55,72,( woh ) hooren ( hain jo ) khaimon mein Mastoor ( hain )
  55,73,to tum apne perwar-digaar ki kon kon si Nemat ko jhutlao ge ?
  55,74,un ko ahal jannat se pehlay nah kisi ensaan ne haath lagaya aur nah kisi jin ne
  55,75,to tum apne perwar-digaar ki kon kon si Nemat ko jhutlao ge ?
  55,76,sabz qalinon aur nafees masnadon par takiya lagaye baithy hon ge
  55,77,to tum apne perwar-digaar ki kon kon si Nemat ko jhutlao ge ?
  55,78,( ae Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihiwasallam ) tumhara perwar-digaar jo sahib jalal vazmt hai is ka naam bara babarkat hai
